lyric: nilnā bihā kull al-muná fī rawḍatin
ṣfart al-‘shī mā āibda‘ ḥusn ābhāhā
ṣfart al-‘shī mā āibda‘ ḥusn ābhāhā
antum surūrī fī al-hawá wajull sulwānī
qad bashsharat biwṣālihā qalbī al-muḥraq qalbī al-muḥraq
wal-shams min min taḥt al-saḥāb ka’annahā
dhahabun taqallab taqallab fī qamīṣin qamīṣin azrq
jā’ al-ḥabīb al-ladhī ahwá min al-safar
wal-shams qad atharat fī khaddih atharā
wal-shams lā yanbaghī an tudrik al-qamar
